text: Ulrich Vite (born 8 February 1944) is a German equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:German male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of East Germany Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Wrocław
